items.headline: Welcome to Bush Whacker 2 wiki
items.desc:
This is a fan-made wiki dedicated to the Facebook (Kongregate and Armor Games) game Bush Whacker 2. We hope the information presented here will help you whack bushes better.

News, updates, tip and tricks.  It is all here and in depth.

Having trouble or problems working your way through the Secret Areas?  Missing out on decortions or Gear items?  Then come to the wiki.
